Keyword	Scope	Reassignment	Redeclaration	Hoisting

var	Function-scoped	âœ… Yes	âœ… Yes	âœ… Hoisted (value = undefined)
let	Block-scoped ({ })	âœ… Yes	âŒ No	âœ… Hoisted (but not initialized)
const	Block-scoped ({ })	âŒ No	âŒ No	âœ… Hoisted (but not initialized)



